FIT with Lan 😤 • How long have I not shared my #workout routine??
Work has been at the top of my list lately but it doesn’t mean slacking on #fitness is an option 🤷🏻‍♀️ When it has become your #lifestyle , it hardly ever stops 💪🏼
—
💥BOSU CHALLENGE💥4 ROUNDS💥
1️⃣ SQUAT x 12
2️⃣ BW SL DEADLIFT x 8 R/L
3️⃣ PUSH-UP x 12
4️⃣ KNEE TO ELBOW x 8 alt R/L
—
🧡 Happy Weekend!! 🧡
—
